register.text: SELECT C.* FROM bookings AS B INNER JOIN schedules AS S ON S.id = B.schedule_id LEFT JOIN fortunetellers AS F ON F.id = S.fortuneteller_id LEFT JOIN call_logs AS C ON C.booking_id = B.id LEFT JOIN analysis_results AS A ON A.call_log_id = C.id INNER JOIN users AS U ON B.user_id = U.id WHERE B.id= 7056 order by B.id desc;
